basics.name: Michael Wybraniec
basics.label: Senior Full-Stack Developer & AI Specialist
basics.summary: Experienced full-stack developer with 10+ years of international experience across 5 countries, specializing in AI integration, Model Context Protocol (MCP), and enterprise solutions. Expert in TypeScript, Python, React, and modern AI frameworks. Founder of ONE-FRONT, delivering cutting-edge AI solutions to businesses worldwide.

work.summary: Founded and leading ONE-FRONT, a boutique development consultancy specializing in AI integration and enterprise solutions. Developed the MCP Resume System, pioneering the use of Model Context Protocol for AI-powered recruitment tools. Delivered projects across multiple industries including fintech, healthcare, and e-commerce. Built AI-powered applications using OpenAI, Anthropic, and local LLM solutions.
highlights: Founded ONE-FRONT, serving international clients across 5 countries
Pioneered MCP Resume System, first-of-its-kind AI recruitment tool
Delivered 50+ successful projects with 99.5% client satisfaction rate
Built AI-powered applications using OpenAI, Anthropic, and local LLM solutions

work.summary: Led development of scalable web applications for Fortune 500 clients. Architected microservices using React, Node.js, and Python. Managed international development teams and implemented DevOps practices including CI/CD pipelines, containerization with Docker, and cloud deployment on AWS. Specialized in real-time applications and API design.
highlights: Led development teams of 10+ developers on enterprise projects
Architected microservices using React, Node.js, and Python
Implemented DevOps practices including CI/CD pipelines
Specialized in real-time applications and API design

work.summary: Developed cutting-edge web applications using modern JavaScript frameworks. Built RESTful APIs and GraphQL services. Worked extensively with cloud platforms (AWS, Azure) and implemented containerization strategies. Contributed to open-source projects and mentored junior developers.
highlights: Developed cutting-edge web applications using modern JavaScript frameworks
Built RESTful APIs and GraphQL services
Contributed to open-source projects with 1000+ GitHub stars
Mentored junior developers

work.summary: Developed web applications using PHP, JavaScript, and MySQL. Worked on e-commerce platforms and content management systems. Gained experience with version control systems, agile methodologies, and collaborative development practices.
highlights: Developed web applications using PHP, JavaScript, and MySQL
Worked on e-commerce platforms and content management systems
Gained experience with version control systems and agile methodologies

highlights: First-of-its-kind AI recruitment tool using MCP
Real-time GitHub gist integration
Multiple LLM provider support (OpenAI, Anthropic, Ollama)
ChatGPT-style interface built with Streamlit
